The paper discusses the rise of socially targeted marketing and the prediction of consumer decisions based on their social networks, which falls under the category of social networks and information retrieval (cs.SI) and social and information networks (cs.SOC). The paper also discusses the adoption of technology, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the use of Caller Ring-Back Tones, which involves cyber-physical systems (cs.CYBER).
